                .selector.plain-reminder-text.col-lg-12.col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
                    p If you can’t find a team member, you’re probably not connected to them or they’re not on Aspire yet.  To connect with someone just go to their profile and click connect.  To invite someone press the big + button on your profile and select ‘Invite someone to Aspire’


            .modal-footer.col-lg-12.col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
                button.btn.btn-default.close-modal(type="button", data-dismiss="modal") Close
                button.btn.btn-default.save-draft(type="button") Save as Draft
                button.btn.btn-default.publish(type="button") Publish